Women's Tennis:

Grand Slam Tournament Champions by Year

Full list of winners, year by year, of the four women's Grand Slam tournaments, this is, all the champions of the Australian Open, the French Open, the US Open and Wimbledon in single competition.

* The French Open became and international event in 1925 and only from that year it is considered a Grand Slam tournament.
